<br>
My character is on the Dawn Server, his name is Raven, he's a Human Elemental Archer, currently level 22.  As much fun as I'm having, I kind of wish I went the Ranger path instead.  A couple of my Ranger friends report having viable healing and buffing ability, which I always wanted.  But then again, I can just level Cleric, too.  Hehe, oh the possibilities!<br>
<br>
Anyway, Raven is in a guild called Illuminati (<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.orion-syndicate.com/illuminati" target="top">link here</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->).  I think they had their roots here in Everquest.  The RP concept behind them is good, and everyone is very friendly, but to be honest the character developement roleplay is lacking in the guild.  I think it's partially because people are still getting used to the game dynamics.  But I have a GREAT storyline going with totally random people I met while adventuring.  It involved a Sslik Spirit Disciple and the fallen Elven city of Feladan, and the wonderful friendship that was formed between him and Raven.<br>
<br>
Well anyway, the real reason I'm here: [<!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/bhorizonsroleplayers" target="top">Horizons Roleplayers</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->].  An RP base for all the roleplayers on Horizons.  Stop on by, say hello, make some friends, and plan some player storylines!<br>
<br>
I highly encourage people to say hello.  I'd love to meet more friends from Firiona Vie.  :-)<br>
<br>
